Quote:  Owing to the inclemency of the weather - the preceding night being "a terror" for wind and rain, when the wind blew as "'twad blawn its last," and the rain fell in torrents, and Friday being also a cold and stormy day (the dark clouds began to disperse and there was a gleam of sunshine about 4 o'clock) - the attendance was not so large as was anticipated.
